menu.name: Vinas Del Vero
menu.description:
Gewurtztraminer White 0,7
A semi-dry wine balanced with a fresh, soft and delicate acidity. Layered with spicy touches typical of the variety and rich in minerals in view of the natural filtration in clay soil. An unforgettable wine that awakens the senses, full of aromas of white roses, honey lychee and maple that accompany the taste in the nose and on the palate, where the wine is velvety and complex. 

0,7

menu.name: Sancerre Pascal Jolivet
menu.description:
Sauvignon Blanc White 0,7
Pascal Giuliba Winery's concept is to produce the wines in the most natural way possible. The grapes undergo natural fermentation at a controlled temperature, without the addition of cultured yeast. The wines of the different soil types are fermented separately to allow the trower to be fully expressed.
